negotiator.config

Class MultilateralTournamentConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.config.MultilateralTournamentConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultilateralTournamentConfigurationInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuiConfiguration

    public class MultilateralTournamentConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultilateralTournamentConfigurationInterface
    Implementation of MultilateralTournamentConfigurationInterface. Extracted from GuiConfiguration. This stores all information for a multilateral tournament. Can be load(File) and save(File) to XML.
    Author:
    W.Pasman 27jul15
